comments: Olynyk (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Green (PHI) and absorbs the contact.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact with Olynyk (MIA) at the end of his drive and does not dislodge him.
Embiid (PHI) is not in the path of Robinson (MIA) when he sets the screen but the contact is marginal.
Herro (MIA) brushes Green's (PHI) arm prior to the start of his upward shooting motion.
During his jump shot attempt, Green (PHI) initiates the contact with Herro (MIA), who is in a legal guarding position.
A 24 second violation is correctly called.
Joe (PHI) dislodges the ball from Vincent (MIA) during his driving shot attempt. Any arm contact after the dislodge is deemed incidental.
Embiid (PHI) makes contact to Achiuwa's (MIA) body after the release that does not affect his play at the basket.
Achiuwa (MIA) makes marginal contact with Embiid (PHI) during the start of his drive that does not cause him to lose control of the ball.
Embiid (PHI) makes incidental contact to Olynyk's (MIA) body and does not dislodge him.
Green (PHI) makes marginal contact with Achiuwa's (MIA) body that does not affect his shot attempt at the rim.
Iguodala (MIA) makes hand on ball contact with Green (PHI) on the perimeter.
Iguodala (MIA) cleanly dislodges the ball from Green (PHI).
Green (PHI) makes incidental contact with Iguodala's (MIA) head as he attempts to get to the loose ball.
Maxey (PHI) makes contact with Herro's (MIA) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Green (PHI) makes clean contact to the ball while defending Herro (MIA) in the backcourt.
Iguodala (MIA) makes incidental contact to Embiid's (PHI) arm during the rebound.
Herro (MIA) cleanly dislodges the ball from Green (PHI) during his jump shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed unsuccessful.  Olynyk (MIA) is not in a legal guarding position and is moving laterally into Embiid's (PHI) path and the contact affects his SQBR.
Iguodala (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Joe (PHI) and absorbs the contact.
Scott (PHI) makes incidental contact to Olynyk's (MIA) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Green (PHI) makes slight contact to Achiuwa's (MIA) arm and does not affect his ability to retain possession of the loose ball.
Green (PHI) and Herro (MIA) make incidental leg contact with each other on the perimeter.
Olynyk (MIA) slightly extends his arms into Joe (PHI) and does not dislodge him during the pick.
Embiid (PHI) dislodges the ball from Achiuwa (MIA) during his shot attempt. While there is additional contact on the play, it?s incidental to his successful block.
Joe (PHI) makes hand on ball contact with Achiuwa (MIA) during his shot attempt underneath the basket.
Joe (PHI) lifts his leg and makes contact to the loose ball.
Vincent (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Green (PHI) and absorbs the contact.
Mathias (PHI) makes contact to Herro's (MIA) lower body that affects his jump shot attempt.
Achiuwa (MIA) attempts to box out Embiid (PHI) during the rebound, but goes underneath him and makes contact to his lower body while he is in the air.
Achiuwa (MIA) makes incidental contact to Green's (PHI) arm after the release that does not affect his play at the basket.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact with Herro (MIA) as he places his hand on his body, removes it, and retreats during his shooting motion on his driving shot attempt.
Achiuwa (MIA) taps the ball when it is outside of the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Achiuwa (MIA) makes incidental contact to Green's (PHI) head during the rebound.
Vincent (MIA) makes slight contact to Green's (PHI) arm after securing the loose ball and does not affect his control of the ball.
Herro (MIA) stops short in Green's (PHI) path but the contact Green makes to Herro's body is marginal.
Green (PHI) makes clean contact to the ball as he tips the pass intended for Herro (MIA).
Herro (MIA) extends his leg as part of a natural shooting motion on the jump shot attempt and the contact with Mathias (PHI) is marginal.
Iguodala (MIA) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
Achiuwa (MIA) grabs Embiid's (PHI) arm and dislodges him from his position during the rebound.
Joe (PHI) makes contact with Robinson's (MIA) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Mathias (PHI) slightly extends his arm into Vincent's (MIA) body and the contact does not dislodge him as Vincent's momentum takes him in the opposite direction of the pass.
Robinson (MIA) grabs Joe's (PHI) arm during the screen that affects his FOM prior to the inbound pass.
Vincent (MIA) commits a take foul on Mathias (PHI).
